node.text: Thank you to everyone who came out to celebrate my PLT collection! node.text: I’m literally crying right now 🥺😭 I couldn’t be in Toronto to celebrate the launch of my global @Puma campaign with my family so puma gave them a special day Downtown to see me up on the big screens. How beautiful is this 😭😍 seeing my mom and my grandparents so proud of their little girl is what really makes everything worth it. Thank you to my @pumasportstyle family for putting this all together and making my family feel so special! I know this is a moment they will never forget! ❤️🥰
